title: Refrigerator Transformer
description: Refrigerator Transformer PartSelect Number PS11738264 Manufacturer Part Number WP11001154 The transformer is for a personal beverage vending machine.

installationInstructions.author: William from Valley City, OH
installationInstructions.title: No Status Lights on Control Board. No 12vdc coming from Transformer.
installationInstructions.content: 1. Unplug power.2. Removed the screws holding on the access panel on rear of machine.3. Remove 4 screws holding plastic cover from motherboard enclosure.4. Replace the transformer and connect wires as they were on the old transformer.6. Replace the cover with the 4 screws.7. Replace the access cover.
